# Opik Integration

When adding LLM calls, always integrate Opik tracing:

Example for Anthropic:
```python
import opik
from opik.integrations.anthropic import track_anthropic

# Wrap the Anthropic client
client = track_anthropic(anthropic.Anthropic())

# Use @opik.track decorator for custom functions
@opik.track
def my_function():
    pass
```

Search the [Opik docs](https://www.comet.com/docs/opik/) for other framework examples
